@folddesc  Contains the sidebar view components, including:
  - VIEW consists of:
    - Backbone Views
  - Model consists of:
    - Backbone Models in /sidebar code
    - HTML5 localStorage in /background
  - Controller:
    - Main controller is in /background
  - VENT: A single Pub/Sub message hub.
  - Messenger:
    - Recieves proxied messages from /background,
      republishes them on vent.
  - Settings:
    - Feature Toggles: Boolean values turn features on/off.
  - extras: shortcuts, text-to-speech, notifications, etc...
